<i>noun</i>: 치욕감 [치욕깜], 치욕 [치욕], 오욕 [오ː욕], 오명 [오ː명], 수치심 [수치심], 수치감 [수치감], 수치 [수치], 불명예 [불명예], 똥칠 [똥칠], 개꼴 [개ː꼴] <i>verb</i>: 먹칠하다 [먹칠하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>치욕감 [치욕깜]</dt><br>
<dd>humiliation; disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>욕되고 창피스러운 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of being dishonored and ashamed.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>치욕 [치욕]</dt><br>
<dd>humiliation; disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>욕되고 창피스러움.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being dishonored and ashamed.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>오욕 [오ː욕]</dt><br>
<dd>disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>명예를 더럽혀 부끄럽고 수치스럽게 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one feels humiliated and embarrassed because one's honor has been damaged or one's name has been tarnished.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>오명 [오ː명]</dt><br>
<dd>bad name; disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>실수나 잘못 등을 해서 더러워지고 부끄럽게 된 이름이나 명예.</dd><br>
<dd>One's name or honor which has become stained or shameful as a result of his/her mistake or fault.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수치심 [수치심]</dt><br>
<dd>shame; humiliation; disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>매우 창피하고 부끄러운 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of being extremely shameful and embarrassed.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수치감 [수치감]</dt><br>
<dd>shame; humiliation; disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>매우 창피하고 부끄러운 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>A feeling of being extremely shameful and embarrassed.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수치 [수치]</dt><br>
<dd>shame; humiliation; disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>매우 창피하고 부끄러움. 또는 그런 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being extremely shameful and embarrassed, or such an event.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>불명예 [불명예]</dt><br>
<dd>dishonor; disgrace; shame</dd><br>
<dd>사람들로부터 높은 평가나 좋은 평판을 받지 못함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of getting a bad reputation or losing respect from people.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>똥칠 [똥칠]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smearing dung</dd><br>
<dd>똥을 묻히는 짓.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of smearing dung.</dd><br>
<dd>2. disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 체면이나 명예를 더럽히는 짓.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) The act of damaging one's reputation or honor.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>개꼴 [개ː꼴]</dt><br>
<dd>disgrace; shame</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 아주 엉망이 된 모양새나 처지.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) An appearance or condition which has gone terribly wrong.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>먹칠하다 [먹칠하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. smear with ink</dd><br>
<dd>먹으로 칠하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To stain something with Chinese ink.</dd><br>
<dd>2. disgrace</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 명예나 체면을 깎아내리는 행위를 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) To tarnish reputation or dignity.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>